### =====================================================================
### 쿠폰 정책 / 선착순 발급 API 테스트 (이슈 #25)
### IntelliJ HTTP Client 형식. 위에서부터 순서대로 실행하면 됩니다.
###
### 사전 준비
###   1) 인프라 기동:   docker compose up -d   (mysql:3307, redis:6379)
###   2) 애플리케이션 기동: ./gradlew bootRun   (기본 포트 8080)
###
### SUPER_ADMIN 시드 (정책 생성 API 는 SUPER_ADMIN 만 허용)
###   회원가입은 항상 BUYER 로 생성되므로, 아래 "관리자 회원가입"(#1) 실행 후
###   DB 에서 역할을 한 번 올려준 뒤 "관리자 로그인"(#3) 을 실행하세요.
###     docker exec -i 11th-street-local-mysql-1 \
###       mysql -urealtime_chat -prealtime_chat realtime_chat \
###       -e "UPDATE member SET role='SUPER_ADMIN' WHERE email='admin01@example.com';"
###
### 멱등성(Request-ID)은 실제 RedisIdempotencyManager(Redis SET NX)로 동작하므로,
### 동일 Request-ID 재시도는 멱등성 단계에서 COUPON_003 으로 차단됩니다.
### 발급 동시성(분산 락)은 RedissonLockManager가 처리하며, 동시성 테스트에서는 LockManager를 목으로 대체합니다.
### =====================================================================

@host = http://localhost:8080
@adminEmail = admin01@example.com
@buyerEmail = buyer01@example.com
@buyer2Email = buyer02@example.com
@password = plainPassword1


### 1. 관리자 회원가입 (201) — 실행 후 위 SQL 로 SUPER_ADMIN 승격 필요
POST {{host}}/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "관리자01"
}


### 2. 구매자 회원가입 (201)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{buyerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "구매자01"
}


### 2-1. 두 번째 구매자 회원가입 (201) — 수량 소진(COUPON_002) 테스트용
POST {{host}}/api/v1/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{buyer2Email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "구매자02"
}


### 3. 관리자 로그인 (200) — accessToken(SUPER_ADMIN) 저장
# @name adminLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert(response.status === 200, "status: " + response.status));
    client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### 4. 구매자 로그인 (200) — accessToken(BUYER) 저장
# @name buyerLogin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{buyerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert(response.status === 200, "status: " + response.status));
    client.global.set("buyerToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### 4-1. 두 번째 구매자 로그인 (200)
# @name buyer2Login
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{buyer2Email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.test("200 OK", () => client.assert(response.status === 200, "status: " + response.status));
    client.global.set("buyer2Token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### =====================================================================
### 쿠폰 정책 등록 (POST /api/v1/coupons, SUPER_ADMIN)
### =====================================================================

### 5. 정책 등록 - 성공: 진행 중(ACTIVE) 정률 + 한도 (201)
# @name createActivePolicy
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "여름맞이 10% 할인",
  "discountType": "PERCENTAGE",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "maxDiscountAmount": 5000,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 1000
}

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
    client.test("상태 ACTIVE", () => client.assert(response.body.data.status === "ACTIVE", "status: " + response.body.data.status));
    client.test("remainingQuantity = totalQuantity", () => client.assert(response.body.data.remainingQuantity === 1000));
    client.global.set("activePolicyId", response.body.data.id);
%}


### 6. 정책 등록 - 성공: 정액(FIXED_AMOUNT), 한도 없음 (201)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "3,000원 정액 할인",
  "discountType": "FIXED_AMOUNT",
  "discountValue": 3000,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 500
}

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
    client.test("maxDiscountAmount null", () => client.assert(response.body.data.maxDiscountAmount === null));
%}


### 7. 정책 등록 - 성공: 시작 전(SCHEDULED) — COUPON_001 테스트용 (201)
# @name createScheduledPolicy
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "다가오는 가을 세일",
  "discountType": "PERCENTAGE",
  "discountValue": 20,
  "maxDiscountAmount": 10000,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-09-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-09-30T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 100
}

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
    client.test("상태 SCHEDULED", () => client.assert(response.body.data.status === "SCHEDULED", "status: " + response.body.data.status));
    client.global.set("scheduledPolicyId", response.body.data.id);
%}


### 8. 정책 등록 - 성공: 잔여 1장(ACTIVE) — COUPON_002 테스트용 (201)
# @name createLastOnePolicy
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "단 한 장 선착순",
  "discountType": "FIXED_AMOUNT",
  "discountValue": 1000,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 1
}

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
    client.global.set("lastOnePolicyId", response.body.data.id);
%}


### 9. 정책 등록 - 실패: BUYER 권한 (403 UNAUTHORIZED_ADMIN)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

{
  "name": "권한없는 등록",
  "discountType": "PERCENTAGE",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 10
}

> {%
    client.test("403 Forbidden", () => client.assert(response.status === 403, "status: " + response.status));
%}


