}

> {%
    client.test("400 Bad Request", () => client.assert(response.status === 400, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 12. 정책 등록 - 실패: 미인증 (401)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "토큰 없음",
  "discountType": "PERCENTAGE",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "issueStartsAt": "2026-06-01T00:00:00",
  "issueEndsAt": "2026-12-31T23:59:59",
  "totalQuantity": 10
}

> {%
    client.test("401 Unauthorized", () => client.assert(response.status === 401, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### =====================================================================
### 선착순 쿠폰 발급 (POST /api/v1/coupons/{couponPolicyId}/issue)
### =====================================================================

### 13. 발급 - 성공: 구매자01, ACTIVE 정책 (201, status ISSUED)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{activePolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0001

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
    client.test("status ISSUED", () => client.assert(response.body.data.status === "ISSUED"));
    client.test("couponPolicyId 일치", () => client.assert(response.body.data.couponPolicyId === client.global.get("activePolicyId")));
%}


### 14. 발급 - 실패: 동일 Request-ID 재시도 (409 COUPON_003)
### (RedisIdempotencyManager가 동일 Request-ID를 멱등성 단계에서 곧바로 COUPON_003 으로 차단합니다.)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{activePolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0001

> {%
    client.test("409 Conflict", () => client.assert(response.status === 409, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 15. 발급 - 실패: 같은 구매자, 다른 Request-ID (409 COUPON_003, 이미 발급)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{activePolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0002

> {%
    client.test("409 Conflict(이미 발급)", () => client.assert(response.status === 409, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 16. 발급 - 실패: 시작 전(SCHEDULED) 정책 (409 COUPON_001)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{scheduledPolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0003

> {%
    client.test("409 Conflict(발급 불가 상태)", () => client.assert(response.status === 409, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 17. 발급 - 성공: 잔여 1장 정책의 마지막 한 장, 구매자01 (201)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{lastOnePolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0004

> {%
    client.test("201 Created", () => client.assert(response.status === 201, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 18. 발급 - 실패: 수량 소진, 구매자02 (409 COUPON_002)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{lastOnePolicyId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyer2Token}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0005

> {%
    client.test("409 Conflict(수량 소진)", () => client.assert(response.status === 409, "status: " + response.status));
