### 19. 발급 - 실패: 미인증 (401)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/{{activePolicyId}}/issue
Request-ID: coupon-req-0006

> {%
    client.test("401 Unauthorized", () => client.assert(response.status === 401, "status: " + response.status));
%}


### 20. 발급 - 실패: 존재하지 않는 정책 (404)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/coupons/999999/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Request-ID: coupon-req-0007

> {%
    client.test("404 Not Found", () => client.assert(response.status === 404, "status: " + response.status));
%}
